,049方呎，實用呎價33,919元。<br />\n對於是次滙控豐取消派息，湯文亮指或多或少都有些耿耿於懷，不過自己自幼於澳門成長，多少有些「賭仔性格」，認為「輸完又嚟賭過，冇乜所謂」。又指雖然可以控告匯豐不派息，但是由於其是以監管機構為由，最終只能浪費彈藥。湯氏指世事難料，若然繼續持有該100萬股滙控豐，現時僅市值4,000餘萬元，但持有物業則可能只是輕微下跌，雖然目前仍然持有數十萬股匯豐，但已經能算是輸少當贏。"},{"pid":"99d8900e70bd05788344d38ae79e111217ed7a15","tid":1953149,"uid":60376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b5b31ef29b344324e62fa46ef28c37f346c43520","tid":1953149,"uid":96465,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"70de007cc7fffa1e16f17e4bbf8d15d4223310f8","tid":1953149,"uid":16775,"like":227,"dislike":2,"score":225,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T04:23:40.000Z","msg":"唔知兩公婆今晚瞓得甜唔甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:07:54.000Z","msg":"共赴黃泉慢慢訓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:26:14.000Z","msg":"咁人地一蚊都無借又唔會死既<br />\n儲得1200萬cash我諗租樓都係濕濕碎je"},{"pid":"f1ac972eccd757b0de9deaea762bae9c4aa8f687","tid":1953149,"uid":46746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:29:52.000Z","msg":"睇佢個名就知佢係on9仔 又大口氣 正一柒頭皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b7dddbeb591b416720c0f78894e5f719067a77","tid":1953149,"uid":144843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:31:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"319e174f2f60f64438cc042e3aaf34e120735850","tid":1953149,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:33:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8025efef3b58b926c2ab18986c31315244a27334","tid":1953149,"uid":29928,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T08:36:08.000Z","msg":"完了吧 如無意外 比無就用淨返d錢 買起個專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd784e22acd3f797ed9f81f9a6421ee0e5275961","tid":1953149,"uid":88848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b5b31ef29b344324e62fa46ef28c37f346c43520","tid":1953149,"uid":96465,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"70de007cc7fffa1e16f17e4bbf8d15d4223310f